      &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/LouisBarranqueiro/hexo-theme-tranquilpeak&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;Tranquilpeak&lt;/a&gt;（宁静）是hexo的一款相比于next更美观，更加图文并茂的主题。&lt;/p&gt;
    
